5000|$|Time diversity: Multiple {{versions}} of the same signal are transmitted at different time instants. Alternatively, a redundant forward <b>error</b> <b>correction</b> <b>code</b> is added and the message is spread in time by means of bit-interleaving before it is transmitted. Thus, error bursts are avoided, which simplifies the error correction.|$|E
